<%- include('partials/header')%>
<!--About Me Section Begins-->
<section class="about">
  <div class="grid-box about-container container">
    <div class="about-heading">
      <h1>Hey! I'm <span class="about-name-highlight">Shalini Thunglano</span></h1>
      <p>I'm an <span class="about-sub-highlight">artist</span> working from <span class="about-sub-highlight">Nagaland, India.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-profile">
      <div class="about-img-container">
        <div class="about-shadow"></div>
        <img src="/assets/images/Shin_About_Cover.jpg" alt="Shin's Profile Image" class="about-img" />
        <div class="about-box"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-info">
      <p class="about-description">
        I am a self taught artist. I have been drawing as a hobby since childhood and when I reflect back its inspiring to know how far I have come.
      </p>
      <p class="about-description">
        I desire to be a blessing with this gift of mine, I am always grateful to my dear ones who have never stopped believing in me.
      </p>
      <p class="about-description">
        My ultimate goal is to inspire, encourage and change lives using this skill. I desire
        to spread hope, comfort and love with my all. Thank you for your support and love on this
        journey of mine! Be blessed.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!--About Me Section Ends-->

<div class="gallery-header glass-bg">
  <h1 class="main-head">A Vision</h1>
</div>

<!--Services Section Begins-->
